$$$ged, $$d quartered. &sect; <HI>XLVII.</HI> The parliament re&s;olve to depo&s;e Edward, and $word$ $is $n to t$e throne. &sect; <HI>XLVIII.</HI> Edward of Caernarvon makes a $word$ r$&s;i$n$ti$n of the $r$w$, $hich $evolvesto his $word$ &sect; <HI>XLIX.</HI> Edward $word$ $ather is $$rb$rcu&s;ly murdered at B$rkeley-ca&s;tle.</P>
